description:
A DLC pack for GROOVE COASTER WAI WAI PARTY!!!! that includes 10 Vocaloid songs, navigators, and avatars!

This pncludes the following content.
■Song Pack (10 songs)
 - NEXT NEST / Satsuki ga Tenkomori
 - Hand in Hand(Magical Mirai ver.) / kz(livetune) 
 - HERO / Ayase
 - Love Trial / 40mP
 - Shoujo Rei / mikitoP
 - Telecaster b boy / THREEE
 - phony / TSUMIKI
 - Surges / Orangestar
 - An Unaware Drunk / Kanaria
 - Kyoufuu Ooru Bakku / Yukopi

■Navigator
 - Hatsune Miku (MagicalMirai2014Ver)
 - Hatsune Miku (MagicalMirai2015Ver)
 - Hatsune Miku (MagicalMirai2023Ver)

■Avatar
 - HATSUNE MIKU(2D,MAGICAL MIRAI 2023)
 - KAGAMINE RIN(2D,MAGICAL MIRAI 2023)
 - KAGAMINE LEN(2D,MAGICAL MIRAI 2023)
 - MEGURINE LUKA(2D,MAGICAL MIRAI 2023)
 - MEIKO(2D,MAGICAL MIRAI 2023)
 - KAITO(2D,MAGICAL MIRAI 2023)

*Some content will be unlocked via missions after downloading.
name: VOCALOID Pack 9
